1.0.0.name: wordpress/annie
1.0.0.description: Annie provides comprehensive annotation options, including footnotes and highlighting. If Tippy is installed, footnotes can be displayed inline using tooltips. Also, footnotes are placed at the end of the post. For highlighting, you are able to use default highlighting styles or define your own.
